    "SteamCMD is only required to download wallpapers. Browsing and viewing details use the Steam Web API." : { "localizations" : { "zh-Hans" : { "stringUnit" : { "state" : "translated", "value" : "仅下载壁纸时需要 SteamCMD；浏览和查看详情使用 Steam Web API。" } } } },
